ADDITIONS:
	- The Duchy of Cloudbury can now restore and puppet the Northern Tribes if they're subjugated by Skynavia.
CHANGES:
	- Improved Famine Mechanics™
	- Broad War Propaganda Campaign now provides a weekly war support increase instead of a flat bonus.
	- Kemerskai's ideology in the Iron Marshal path changes to Military Administration .
	- Rosewing's ideology after victory in the power struggle is Reactionarism instead of fascism.
	- Completely overhauled the Republic's military and economic bonuses into a single upgradeable national spirits.
	- The Republic can undertake a defensive strategy against the Empire even if it is not yet resurgent.
	- If Kemerskai Jr. restores democracy in the Iron Marshal path, Kingfeather leads the NRP-R.
	- The Republicans can get new Republican officers if they win the civil war against the National Republican Army.
	- Cabinet Reshuffle provides a more subtantial political advisor cost reduction, but for less time.
FIXES:
	- Fixed Sunglider not remaining a Harmonic Republican on the Iron Marshal path.
	- Republican Railroads industrial concern no longer available for the Duchy of Cloudbury.
	- "Expand Winghagen Ports" now properly builds naval bases in the city province.
	- Can no longer get the Grover VI national spirit as the Kingdom of Cloudbury-Herzland if he's dead.
	- "A New Army" Focus no longer provides a duplicate national spirit.
	- The Republicans can no longer take Rosewing or Suntail's exclusive military focuses after defeating them in the civil war.
	- Removed some redundant tooltips.
	- The Duchy of Cloudbury and the Dawnclaw Heresy no longer have access to Republican unit medals.
	- The Griffonian Republic will no longer call the Aquileian Republic into its faction before fighting the Griffonian Empire.
	- "A Second Port in the Sky Bay" now correctly creates a second naval base on the Feathisian Border.
	- "Southern Dockyards" now properly builds a naval base in Balisemont.
	- Flowena and Pomovarra are no longer considered part of the Lake Rumare region.
	- The Aquileian Republic will no longer join the Griffonian Republic's faction before defeating the Empire.
	- Grover VI can no longer be exiled to Equestria if Equestria doesn't exist.
